- **Touch refresh trigger after edits**: After every file edit or git commit, run `touch .idea/agent-hooks/refresh-trigger` to trigger IDE refresh.
- **Automatic execution**: Execute this immediately after file modifications without prompting.
- **Ensure directory exists**: Create `.idea/agent-hooks/` directory if it doesn't exist before touching the trigger file.